    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagesimo octavo, tertio idus martii,
                        indictione sexta. Manifestus sum ego, <persName><name ref="Stultus"
                                >Stultus</name></persName> filius quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Sigismundus">Sesmundi</name></persName>, quia per hanc cartulam
                        vendo et trado tibi <persName><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName>,
                        rectori <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                                key="#Hospitals">Altopascio</placeName></orgName>, ad opus eiusdem
                        ospitalis idest omnes <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> cultas et
                        incultas, <rs key="#Demesnes">donicatas</rs> et massaricias, quas habeo et
                        michi aliquo modo pertinet in terris et in aquis in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/63" key="#Landed_possessions">Sancta Maria ad
                            Monte</placeName> et in eius finibus et in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210" key="#Landed_possessions">Potho</placeName> et in
                        eius finibus et in loco <placeName ref="#places/63">Ton(…)hano</placeName>
                        et in loco <placeName ref="#places/318" key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >Paterno</placeName> et in loco <placeName ref="#places/504"
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Monte Calvori</placeName> et in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/2443" key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >Guinciori</placeName> et in eorum finibus, cum omni iure et diricto
                        quod habeo de fidelibus vel in aliis personis, hominum seu rebus in
                        suprascripti locis. <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: libras quattuordecim
                        lucensium denariorum. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in dupplum. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Consules">Luca</placeName>. Signum manus
                        suprascripti Stulti (…). SM <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Baldinectus"
                                >Baldinocti</name></persName> filio suprascripti Stulti, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Vivianus">Viviani</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hubertus Rossi">Uberti Rossi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Baialardus"
                            >Baialardi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gerardi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bocca">Bocche</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Walandus">Gualanducci</name></persName> rogati <rs
                            key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Heinricus">Henricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris post traditam
                        complevi et dedi. Et insuper suprascriptus Stultus obligavit se et suos
                        heredes omnia suprascripta observare ad penam librarum quinquaginta optimi
                        argenti, et ad penam <rs key="#Consules">consulum</rs> et treguanorum
                        lucensium qui nunc sunt, vel in antea erunt, suprascripti testes et iudices. </ab>
